text: Tahquitz is the name of a shaman, and spirit, of Cahuilla Indian legend. Tahquitz might also refer to: *Tahquitz Canyon, a canyon near Palm Springs, California said to be home to Tahquitz of legend **Tahquitz Creek, the creek that runs through the canyon **Tahquitz Falls, water falls in the canyon *Tahquitz Peak, a peak in Southern California's San Jacinto Mountain Range. **Lily Rock or Tahquitz Rock, a granite outcrop on the side of Tahquitz peak
title: Tahquitz (disambiguation)
